Package backend

Class Record

java.lang.Object
backend.Record
public class Record
extends java.lang.Object
This is the class used to hold crime records in the application. It is also used for display in the main TableView. Record is constructed using a list of Strings. A Record object can be converted into one comma separated String or a list of Strings using the provided methods.
